      "full_name": "Joint Stock Company “Scientific Production Enterprise ‘Rubin’”",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "JSC “Scientific Production Enterprise ‘Rubin’” is a leading company of the Russian defence industry which manufactures mobile automated control and communication systems designed for military applications. The company holds an active State licence in Russia for the maintenance and servicing of weapons and military equipment. It plays a significant role in the supply chain of the Russian Armed Forces, supplying them with specialised military equipment. Among the various systems produced for the Russian army is the air defence control system “Magistr-SV”, which has been deployed in the context of Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}